00:15:23,370 --> 00:15:24,770
Stop messing around.

190
00:15:24,770 --> 00:15:26,940
Come, I'll toast you.

191
00:15:32,000 --> 00:15:34,230
Get a fruit.

192
00:15:38,900 --> 00:15:42,300
All right. I'll get a fruit.

