211
00:19:04,300 --> 00:19:06,600
Look at her.

212
00:19:09,700 --> 00:19:12,260
Allow me to toast you.

213
00:19:16,800 --> 00:19:20,940
- Eat some more.
- Sure.

214
00:19:20,940 --> 00:19:22,430
Nice!

215
00:19:25,000 --> 00:19:28,020
