219
00:19:44,620 --> 00:19:46,290
Now you want me to stay?

220
00:19:46,290 --> 00:19:48,240
Are you in cahoots to play me?

221
00:19:48,240 --> 00:19:51,060
Miss, stop being angry.

222
00:19:51,060 --> 00:19:54,340
Mister also has his difficulties.

223
00:19:54,340 --> 00:19:58,470
