224
00:19:58,470 --> 00:20:01,800
But I really have to tell you something.

225
00:20:01,800 --> 00:20:03,620
What is it?

226
00:20:06,300 --> 00:20:10,600
Do you remember that night when he went to find the Earth Absorbing Bell for you?

227
00:20:12,300 --> 00:20:14,480
You only know that he found it,

228
00:20:14,480 --> 00:20:20,810
but you didn't know he was badly hurt after receiving three punches from First Princess.

229
00:20:20,810 --> 00:20:23,380
